parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger occupancy mat sensor can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of an accident, potentially leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The passenger restraint system malfunction warning light comes on
even when there is no passenger in the seat; the warning light turns off and on randomly; the error message "PASSENGER RESTRAINT MALFUNCTION" appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to rupture, potentially leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The vehicle remains subject to an airbag inflator recall
blocking resale or trade-in; the part to repair the recall is unavailable; the manufacturer exceeds a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The drivetrain malfunction and engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. This issue can also cause the vehicle to stall while driving, which can increase the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The drivetrain malfunction warning light appears on the dashboard
the vehicle slows down or loses power
the vehicle stalls while driving
the vehicle goes into limp mode
the engine shuts off
the vehicle accelerates unexpectedly
the vehicle shakes or vibrates violently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the engine to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The drivetrain malfunction warning light appears on the dashboard
the vehicle slows down or loses power
the engine shuts off
the vehicle stalls while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. This issue can also cause the vehicle to stall while driving, which can increase the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The drivetrain malfunction warning light appears on the dashboard
the vehicle slows down or loses power
the vehicle stalls while driving
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle goes into limp mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to exit the vehicle, which can lead to safety issues, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: Doors do not open when attempting to exit the vehicle
doors unlock but do not open
doors can only be opened with the key hole or from inside the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Loss of Power and Engine Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of power and engine malfunction can cause the vehicle to suddenly lose power, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Loss of power
vehicle will not rev past 2500 RPM
radiator fan goes to max and cuts off consistently
engine oil temperature is lower than normal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the horn can cause the driver to be unable to warn other drivers of potential hazards, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Horn does not work when the car is turned off
horn only works when the key is in the ignition and the start button is pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag and safety system can cause the airbags to fail to deploy in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag deployment error
airbags did not deploy in the event of an accident
electrical wires for the computer system are behind the rear tail light and can be damaged in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the auto start/stop function can cause the vehicle to not start again, which can lead to safety issues, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: Auto start/stop function has malfunctioned
vehicle does not start again after stopping
error message "ignition malfunction -- do not turn engine off" appears.
